snippet.title: Enigma of Sépia Official Trailer
snippet.description:
"Where darkness reigns, we shall stand to defy it!"

Prepare to enter the world of Enigma of Sépia—a next-gen RPG with breathtaking world-building and revolutionary gameplay that lets you level up any hero to SSR+.
The journey begins on February 14th, 2025.
For the Void City!

Pre-register Now: https://app.enigmaofsepia.com/P5gu/trailer
